  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong><i>TRYP FPV</i></strong>, immerse yourself in the most <strong>realistic FPV flying experience</strong> ever created. Designed for all levels of pilots, this <strong>simulator </strong>pushes the boundaries of <strong>realism </strong>with stunning graphics and <strong>ultra-accurate flight sensations</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully experience the adrenaline of FPV drone flying with no limits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/c1a08950e2ff4ce64c16ee31e6651aff.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/c1a08950e2ff4ce64c16ee31e6651aff.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/c1a08950e2ff4ce64c16ee31e6651aff.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMMERSIVE FLIGHT SENSATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the thrill of controlling an FPV drone like never before, thanks to ultra-realistic flight simulation manage with the PID loop :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inertia and gravity management: </strong>Every turn and speed change has been fine-tuned so your drone responds as it would in real-life conditions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Optimized aerodynamics: </strong>Wind effects, air resistance, and acceleration are carefully calibrated using digital twin technology to replicate the authentic sensation of flying outdoors.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic sound design:</strong> Every engine sound and gust of wind is crafted to enhance the feeling of immersion.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/bb40e68410c84ecbb0537a4d6eea0e27.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/bb40e68410c84ecbb0537a4d6eea0e27.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/bb40e68410c84ecbb0537a4d6eea0e27.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REALISTIC ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a wide range of spots scanned from real-world locations flown by pilots from around the globe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 5 high-quality maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through the pyramids, cross urban bandos, weave between palm trees, ski down slopes, or slalom between skyscrapers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/f6f07ecdf9c7b16ed77eeb60fbd4c646.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/f6f07ecdf9c7b16ed77eeb60fbd4c646.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/f6f07ecdf9c7b16ed77eeb60fbd4c646.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VARIED GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments in long-range with the <strong>TRYP Mode. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your skills in freestyle with <strong>CHALLENGE Mode.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the camera in <strong>SCENARIO Mode.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against the best pilots in <strong>RACE Mode </strong>and climb to the top of the global leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/6ad2a85cc73fb36d221c8ae8bcb33347.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/6ad2a85cc73fb36d221c8ae8bcb33347.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/6ad2a85cc73fb36d221c8ae8bcb33347.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTREME CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TRYP FPV offers advanced drone customization for complete control over your flying experience:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust your rates to refine the responsiveness and fluidity of your controls.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your dream drone by selecting from a range of frames, propellers, batteries (LiPo), and cameras, creating a setup that fits you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the angle and settings of your camera for optimal immersion, whether for freestyle or racing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/fe9bd1c7638b17905dc29e36d8e67040.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/fe9bd1c7638b17905dc29e36d8e67040.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/fe9bd1c7638b17905dc29e36d8e67040.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong><i>TRYP FPV</i></strong>, immerse yourself in the most <strong>realistic FPV flying experience</strong> ever created. Designed for all levels of pilots, this <strong>simulator </strong>pushes the boundaries of <strong>realism </strong>with stunning graphics and <strong>ultra-accurate flight sensations</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully experience the adrenaline of FPV drone flying with no limits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/c1a08950e2ff4ce64c16ee31e6651aff.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/c1a08950e2ff4ce64c16ee31e6651aff.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/c1a08950e2ff4ce64c16ee31e6651aff.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMMERSIVE FLIGHT SENSATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the thrill of controlling an FPV drone like never before, thanks to ultra-realistic flight simulation manage with the PID loop :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inertia and gravity management: </strong>Every turn and speed change has been fine-tuned so your drone responds as it would in real-life conditions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Optimized aerodynamics: </strong>Wind effects, air resistance, and acceleration are carefully calibrated using digital twin technology to replicate the authentic sensation of flying outdoors.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic sound design:</strong> Every engine sound and gust of wind is crafted to enhance the feeling of immersion.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/bb40e68410c84ecbb0537a4d6eea0e27.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/bb40e68410c84ecbb0537a4d6eea0e27.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/bb40e68410c84ecbb0537a4d6eea0e27.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REALISTIC ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a wide range of spots scanned from real-world locations flown by pilots from around the globe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 5 high-quality maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through the pyramids, cross urban bandos, weave between palm trees, ski down slopes, or slalom between skyscrapers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/f6f07ecdf9c7b16ed77eeb60fbd4c646.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/f6f07ecdf9c7b16ed77eeb60fbd4c646.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/f6f07ecdf9c7b16ed77eeb60fbd4c646.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VARIED GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments in long-range with the <strong>TRYP Mode. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your skills in freestyle with <strong>CHALLENGE Mode.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the camera in <strong>SCENARIO Mode.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against the best pilots in <strong>RACE Mode </strong>and climb to the top of the global leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/6ad2a85cc73fb36d221c8ae8bcb33347.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/6ad2a85cc73fb36d221c8ae8bcb33347.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/6ad2a85cc73fb36d221c8ae8bcb33347.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTREME CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TRYP FPV offers advanced drone customization for complete control over your flying experience:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust your rates to refine the responsiveness and fluidity of your controls.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your dream drone by selecting from a range of frames, propellers, batteries (LiPo), and cameras, creating a setup that fits you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the angle and settings of your camera for optimal immersion, whether for freestyle or racing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/fe9bd1c7638b17905dc29e36d8e67040.poster.avif?t=1766077575\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/fe9bd1c7638b17905dc29e36d8e67040.webm?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881200/extras/fe9bd1c7638b17905dc29e36d8e67040.mp4?t=1766077575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
